user_query: Show all shipments going to San Diego

llm_cypher: MATCH (s:Shipment)-[:ASSIGNED_TO]->(:Courier {name: 'ParcelPro'}) WHERE s.delivery_date > s.expected_delivery_date RETURN s.tracking_number

user_query: Show all SwiftExpress shipments to Atlanta
Find shipments going from Miami to Boston
List shipments with duplicate tracking numbers
llm_cypher: MATCH (s1:Shipment), (s2:Shipment) WHERE s1.tracking_number = s2.tracking_number AND s1<>s2 RETURN s1.tracking_number
MATCH (s:Shipment) WHERE date(s.delivery_date).dayOfWeek IN [6, 7] RETURN s.tracking_number

user_query: Show customers with shipments handled by multiple couriers
llm_cypher: MATCH (s:Shipment)-[:ASSIGNED_TO]->(c:Courier) WITH s.customer AS customer, COLLECT(DISTINCT c.name) AS couriers WHERE size(couriers) > 1 RETURN customer
